      <title>拜登斥资 110 亿美元在芯片研发领域击败中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/biden-makes-11-billion-push-to-beat-china-at-chip-research</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府振兴芯片行业的努力主要集中在为国内工厂提供数十亿美元的补助。但这一推动还有一个较少被讨论的方面：将尖端半导体研究变成对美国人来说更有吸引力的领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/biden-makes-11-billion-push-to-beat-china-at-chip-research</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
